* Explore & Discover\nDatabase Objects
** Catalog Explorer
***_ Columns, Sample Data, Details
***_ History tab (Delta tables)
***_ Insights: queries & users (30 days)
***_ View relationships (ERD)
** SQL Commands
***_ SHOW CATALOGS / SCHEMAS / TABLES
***_ DESCRIBE TABLE EXTENDED
***_ SHOW COLUMNS / TBLPROPERTIES
***_ Pattern matching with LIKE
** Tag Search
***_ Workspace search bar
***_ Search by tag key or value
***_ Requires BROWSE privilege
